sourcesContent:
export const homeOjbOne = {
    lightBg: true,
    primary: false,
    topLine: "A Masters In Artificial Inteligence Student At Northeastern.",
    lightTopLine: false,
    lightText: false,
    lightTextDesc: false,
    headline: "Hi! I'm Parijat Chatterjee.",
    description: "I have been a Machine Learning enthusiast for a long time, which has led me to several internships. I recently took the next big step by enrolling in the Northeastern University's Masters in Artificial Intelligence program in Boston. Apart from all that time I have been spending on artificial brains, you can find me learning about finance, going on treks or trying my hand in cooking. I love meeting new people, so please feel free to get in touch!",
    buttonLabel: 'LinkedIn',
    img: require("../images/profile.svg").default,
    alt: "Their should be an image here",
    imgStart: '',
    start: '',
    link: 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/parijat-chatterjee/',
    btn: true,
    lst: false
  };
  
  
  export const homeOjbTwo = {
    lightBg: false,
    primary: false,
    topLine: "What I've been working on.",
    lightTopLine: false,
    lightText: true,
    lightTextDesc: true,
    headline: "Recent Projects",
    description: "I have worked with numerous training and inference pipelines such as face recognition, object detection, and GANs. I also have experience deploying them on various types of computing platforms. I have extensively used several Deep Learning libraries and toolkits such as PyTorch and TensorFlow to solve engineering problems involving Computer Vision and Natural Language Processing. ",
    buttonLabel: "SEE MORE OF MY WORK.",
    img: false,
    alt: "Their should be an image here",
    imgStart: 'start',
    start: 'true',
    link: 'https://github.com/killerpanda101',
    btn: true, 
    lst: true,
    lstType: 'proj'
  };
  
  export const homeOjbThree = {
    lightBg: true,
    primary: false,
    topLine: "Things i have been reading.",
    lightTopLine: false,
    lightText: false,
    lightTextDesc: false,
    headline: "Articles",
    description: "I have recently been working on some original content and hope to have that up soon on my Medium profile. Until then, here are some of my favorite articles from my Medium reading list.",
    buttonLabel: "SEE ALL ON MEDIUM",
    img: false,
    alt: "Their should be an image here",
    imgStart: "",
    start: "",
    link: 'https://medium.com/@parijat.chatterjee13/list/reading-list',
    btn: true,
    lst: true,
    lstType: 'article'
  };
  
  export const homeOjbFour = {
    lightBg: false,
    primary: false,
    topLine: "I'd love to hear about you :-)",
    lightTopLine: false,
    lightText: true,
    lightTextDesc: true,
    headline: "LET'S BE INTERNET FRIENDS",
    description: "If you want to ask me questions about anything (really anything, I love to chat) or just want to get in touch, feel free to reach out on LinkedIn or drop me an email at chatterjee.pa@northeastern.edu and I will get back to you asap.",
    buttonLabel: "",
    img: false,
    alt: "Their should be an image here",

    lst: true,
    lstType: 'social'
  };
